OF
Sundry Tran&s;actions
FROM THE
<HI>World in the Moon.</HI></P>
<P>$ran&s;lated from the Lunar
LANGUAGE,
By the AUTHOR of
<HI>The True-born Engli&s;h Man.</HI></P>
<P><HI>LONDON:</HI>
