it would be to them that &s;tay'd behind.</ITEM>
<PB N="33" REF="35">
<ITEM>3. That it is not to be wonder'd at, why
the <HI>Chine&s;e</HI> excell &s;o much all the&s;e Parts
of the World, &s;ince but for that Know|ledge
